This git repo was made with:
git clone -o upstream git://git.debian.org/git/kernel/initramfs-tools.git

In order to be able to fetch/merge upstream with git-fetch and git-merge (repectively), you need your .git/config as such:

[remote "upstream"]
	url = git://git.debian.org/git/kernel/initramfs-tools.git
	fetch = +refs/heads/*:refs/remotes/upstream/*
[branch "debian"]
	remote = upstream
	merge = refs/heads/master
